-- Germany Plans Nuclear ‘Ethics Commission,’ Sueddeutsche Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-01-24T06:29:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/germany-plans-nuclear-ethics-commission-sueddeutsche-reports.html
Germany  will introduce an “ethics
commission” in its search for a place to deposit nuclear waste
from its reactors,  Sueddeutsche Zeitung  reported today, without
saying where it obtained the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
